<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 4 (Ruca) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スパーダ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Spada</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルカ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ruca</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ンだよ、この無駄な大冒険。
終わりが見えねェ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the heck is up with this
useless grand adventure?
Ain't no end in sight...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ご、ごめんね。
いつの間にかこんな事になっちゃって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I'm sorry. This is just how it
ended up before I even realized...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ったく。
マジでお前はしょうがねェヤツだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeesh. You seriously are a lost cause.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……ごめん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Sorry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>謝ってんじゃねぇよ。
お前のそういうとこだけは
悪くねェと思ってんだからよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't apologize for it. Heck, I think that's
the one about ya that ain't even bad.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>行くぜ、ルカ！
イケてるだかコケてるだか知らねぇが
鳥退治によ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go, Ruca! Heck if I know if we're gonna look
cool doin' this or if we're gonna flop like
dumbasses, but it's bird extermination time!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Not sure if 鳥退治 is literal here.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
